Although cross-country bikes aren't
designed specifically for technical

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:07.300
trails, one look at the very best
cross-country riders shows they're more

00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:09.712
than fast enough.
So what are the secrets?

00:00:09.712 --> 00:00:12.235
Well, here are five things for you
to work at.

